+            if stdout and not stderr:

+                else:
+                    match_count += 0
+            if stderr:
+                failed = True
+                out_dict["stderr"].append({str(pcap.pcap_file): stdout.decode().replace("pcap DAQ configured to read-file.", "").split("Finished rule args:")[-1]})
+        except Exception as e:
